---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Button from '../components/Button.astro';

const metaDescription = "Contactez le Salon VK Secrets à Strasbourg Neuhof. Téléphone, WhatsApp pro, réseaux sociaux. Adresse : 85 Rte d’Altenheim. Nouveaux horaires : lun & jeu-ven jusqu’à 20 h 30.";
---

<Layout 
  title="Contact" 
  description={metaDescription}
>
  <section class="pt-20 pb-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-12">
        <h1 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl mb-2 text-accent-900">Contactez le Salon VK Secrets</h1>
        <h2 class="font-script text-2xl mb-6 text-accent-700">& Prenez Rendez-Vous</h2>
        <p class="text-text-medium">
          Pour toute question ou pour prendre rendez-vous, n'hésitez pas à me contacter.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Contact Info -->
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-soft p-8">
          <div class="mb-8">
            <h3 class="font-display text-xl mb-6 text-accent-900 border-b border-primary-200 pb-2">Informations de Contact</h3>
            
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-4">
              <div class="bg-primary-100 rounded-full p-3 text-accent-700">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-medium text-accent-900 mb-1">Téléphone</h4>
                <p class="text-text-medium mb-1">Prise de rendez-vous par téléphone/réseaux sociaux</p>
                <a href="tel:+33783960543" class="text-xl font-medium text-accent-500 hover:text-accent-700 transition-colors">
                  07 83 96 05 43
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-4">
              <div class="bg-primary-100 rounded-full p-3 text-accent-700">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-medium text-accent-900 mb-1">Email</h4>
                <p class="text-text-medium mb-1">Pour les informations générales (réponse sous 48h)</p>
                <a href="mailto:salonvksecrets@gmail.com" class="text-accent-700 hover:text-accent-900 transition-colors">
                  salonvksecrets@gmail.com
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
              <div class="bg-primary-100 rounded-full p-3 text-accent-700">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z" />
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z" />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h4 class="font-medium text-accent-900 mb-1">Adresse</h4>
                <p class="text-text-medium mb-1">Au sein de Candem Coiffure</p>
                <address class="not-italic">
                  85 Route d'Altenheim<br>
                  67100 Strasbourg<br>
                  Quartier Neuhof
                </address>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-xl mb-6 text-accent-900 border-b border-primary-200 pb-2">Horaires d'Ouverture</h3>
            <p class="mb-4 font-medium text-accent-700">Uniquement sur Rendez-vous</p>
            <ul class="space-y-2">
              <li class="flex justify-between">
                <span>Lundi</span>
                <span>10h - 20h30</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex justify-between">
                <span>Mardi</span>
                <span>10h - 17h</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex justify-between">
                <span>Mercredi</span>
                <span class="text-primary-500 font-medium">Fermé</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex justify-between">
                <span>Jeudi</span>
                <span>10h - 20h30h</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex justify-between">
                <span>Vendredi</span>
                <span>10h - 20h30</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex justify-between">
                <span>Samedi</span>
                <span class="text-primary-500 font-medium">Sur demande</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex justify-between">
                <span>Dimanche</span>
                <span class="text-primary-500 font-medium">Sur demande</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <div class="mt-8">
            <h3 class="font-display text-xl mb-6 text-accent-900 border-b border-primary-200 pb-2">Réseaux Sociaux</h3>
            <div class="flex space-x-4">
              <a 
                href="https://www.facebook.com/salonvksecrets" 
                target="_blank" 
                rel="noopener noreferrer" 
                class="flex items-center gap-2 text-accent-700 hover:text-accent-900 transition-colors"
              >
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path d="M9 8h-3v4h3v12h5v-12h3.642l.358-4h-4v-1.667c0-.955.192-1.333 1.115-1.333h2.885v-5h-3.808c-3.596 0-5.192 1.583-5.192 4.615v3.385z"/>
                </svg>
                Facebook
              </a>
              <a 
                href="https://www.instagram.com/salonvksecrets" 
                target="_blank" 
                rel="noopener noreferrer" 
                class="flex items-center gap-2 text-accent-700 hover:text-accent-900 transition-colors"
              >
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path d="M12 2.163c3.204 0 3.584.012 4.85.07 3.252.148 4.771 1.691 4.919 4.919.058 1.265.069 1.645.069 4.849 0 3.205-.012 3.584-.069 4.849-.149 3.225-1.664 4.771-4.919 4.919-1.266.058-1.644.07-4.85.07-3.204 0-3.584-.012-4.849-.07-3.26-.149-4.771-1.699-4.919-4.92-.058-1.265-.07-1.644-.07-4.849 0-3.204.013-3.583.07-4.849.149-3.227 1.664-4.771 4.919-4.919 1.266-.057 1.645-.069 4.849-.069zm0-2.163c-3.259 0-3.667.014-4.947.072-4.358.2-6.78 2.618-6.98 6.98-.059 1.281-.073 1.689-.073 4.948 0 3.259.014 3.668.072 4.948.2 4.358 2.618 6.78 6.98 6.98 1.281.058 1.689.072 4.948.072 3.259 0 3.668-.014 4.948-.072 4.354-.2 6.782-2.618 6.979-6.98.059-1.28.073-1.689.073-4.948 0-3.259-.014-3.667-.072-4.947-.196-4.354-2.617-6.78-6.979-6.98-1.281-.059-1.69-.073-4.949-.073zm0 5.838c-3.403 0-6.162 2.759-6.162 6.162s2.759 6.163 6.162 6.163 6.162-2.759 6.162-6.163c0-3.403-2.759-6.162-6.162-6.162zm0 10.162c-2.209 0-4-1.79-4-4 0-2.209 1.791-4 4-4s4 1.791 4 4c0 2.21-1.791 4-4 4zm6.406-11.845c-.796 0-1.441.645-1.441 1.44s.645 1.44 1.441 1.44c.795 0 1.439-.645 1.439-1.44s-.644-1.44-1.439-1.44z"/>
                </svg>
                Instagram
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Map and Contact Form -->
        <div>
          <!-- Map -->
          <div class="mb-8">
            <h3 class="font-display text-xl mb-4 text-accent-900">Nous Trouver</h3>
            <div class="aspect-video rounded-lg overflow-hidden shadow-soft">
              <iframe 
                src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d2641.111522905694!2d7.7415!3d48.55!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x4796c9d3b6a34d4d%3A0x7b6cdc47b46f3ef!2s85%20Rte%20d&#39;Altenheim%2C%2067100%20Strasbourg!5e0!3m2!1sfr!2sfr!4v1627040283088!5m2!1sfr!2sfr" 
                width="100%" 
                height="100%" 
                style="border:0;" 
                allowfullscreen="" 
                loading="lazy"
                title="Google Maps - Localisation du Salon VK Secrets"
              ></iframe>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Contact Form -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-soft p-8">
            <h3 class="font-display text-xl mb-6 text-accent-900">Formulaire de Contact</h3>
            <p class="text-text-medium mb-6">
              Pour toute question générale, vous pouvez nous contacter via ce formulaire.
              <span class="font-medium block mt-2 text-primary-500">Pour les rendez-vous, veuillez appeler au 07 83 96 05 43.</span>
            </p>
            
            <form class="space-y-4" action="https://formspree.io/f/mrbqqowl" method="POST">
              <div>
                <label for="name" class="block mb-1 text-text-medium">Nom</label>
                <input 
                  type="text" 
                  id="name" 
                  name="name" 
                  required
                  class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-200 rounded-md focus:ring-primary-300 focus:border-primary-300"
                />
              </div>
              
              <div>
                <label for="email" class="block mb-1 text-text-medium">Email</label>
                <input 
                  type="email" 
                  id="email" 
                  name="email" 
                  required
                  class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-200 rounded-md focus:ring-primary-300 focus:border-primary-300"
                />
              </div>
              
              <div>
                <label for="phone" class="block mb-1 text-text-medium">Téléphone</label>
                <input 
                  type="tel" 
                  id="phone" 
                  name="phone"
                  class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-200 rounded-md focus:ring-primary-300 focus:border-primary-300"
                />
              </div>
              
              <div>
                <label for="message" class="block mb-1 text-text-medium">Message</label>
                <textarea 
                  id="message" 
                  name="message" 
                  rows="5" 
                  required
                  class="w-full px-4 py-2 border border-gray-200 rounded-md focus:ring-primary-300 focus:border-primary-300"
                ></textarea>
              </div>
              
              <div class="text-sm text-text-light">
                <p>En soumettant ce formulaire, j'accepte que mes informations soient utilisées uniquement pour me recontacter et ne seront pas conservées au-delà de la nécessité de traiter ma demande.</p>
              </div>
              
              <Button type="submit" variant="primary" class="w-full">
                Envoyer le Message
              </Button>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>